{"tid":1632473,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[case study]  揸車hit and run罪大惡極","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:47:33.000Z","uid":251732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dac4ce9826f527d99c4002e0060e1dcb7638ccc2","tid":1632473,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"見個的士佬開車撞小朋友畀人獅鳥都算係溫和咗， 用返西方標準對待汽車hit and run屠殺係會consider為恐怖主義。<br />\n 特別係2017年八月美國charlottesville 極右集會期間，一個白人至上肥閪James Alex Fields Jr.揸住架汽車撞向反極右集會遊行隊伍入面，結果撞死咗女示威者Heather Heyer同撞殘幾個示威者幾個之餘， 更加比美國聯邦法院判處419年嘅終生監禁兼不得假釋， 就係因為佢犯案動機係建基於對民主人權價值觀嘅鄙視同仇恨， 佢呢啲仆街所信仰嘅價值觀同而家 Chinazi嘅意識形態大同小異！<br />\n所以下次再有仆街司機想搞汽車恐怖主義嘅話，就唔好淨係召喚神獸咁簡單， 必須用盡一切手段唔好畀佢哋喺社會上有立足之地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n驅逐共黨 解放香港<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光<br />\n香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"44a1363f442f945a4eee5d748d3ea542c6887d24","tid":1632473,"uid":167758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"612721811831929101"},{"pid":"3f61034dc8b7e1fda5ca8aa63bfd6627687291dd","tid":1632473,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a1363f442f945a4eee5d748d3ea542c6887d24","tid":1632473,"uid":167758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"612721811831929101"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記被困喺鐵籠入面嘅小朋友"},{"pid":"68c03c19bd3fecf18c922ab41e4b62acb4cabbe1","tid":1632473,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"trump 話係antifa 挑釁司機在先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898debeef0a1a7083575be8c302f47c37415a0e9","tid":1632473,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit